# NestJS

> Progressive Node.js framework for building efficient, scalable server-side applications with TypeScript.

---

## Overview

NestJS combines OOP, FP, and FRP principles:
- **Modular Architecture**: Organized with modules, like Angular
- **Dependency Injection**: Built-in IoC container
- **TypeScript First**: Full type safety out of the box
- **Decorators**: Express intent declaratively
- **Testing**: Built-in testing utilities

---

## Why NestJS

| vs Express | vs Fastify Raw |
|------------|----------------|
| Structured architecture | Built-in DI |
| TypeScript native | Modular organization |
| Built-in validation | Enterprise patterns |
